  ('0390ec9c-0cbe-4e4b-a398-b424760f55e0','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',50.0,'Willie Griffin Jr. ~58 (founded 2004); pre-aging-out window; 22yr tenure.',60.0,'Solo FDL + single Lubbock location; small family-owned $1-3M; Tukios platform.',40.0,'Modern Tukios platform; BBB-accredited; active obits = NOT coasting; 22yrs too short for sweet-spot exhaustion.',78.0,'Lubbock tier-2; W TX market.',54.0,'C_watch','22yr Lubbock FH. Owner est ~58yr. C-tier.','C-tier WATCH. Recheck in 5-7 yrs as owner enters 60s.','low',0.55),
  ('fa29ca1d-e649-45c5-a849-e997d4c5def0','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',15.0,'Owner ~44 (blog 2011 age 29); far below aging-out window; hard gate <53 → ≤35 cap.',65.0,'Solo FDL + crematory; single Sugar Land location; $1.5-3M est.',25.0,'Owner built palatial facility from ground up; previously 2 facilities Oakland CA; well-capitalized growth-mode; modern operations.',88.0,'Sugar Land Houston metro affluent suburb +5.',41.0,'D_pass','16yr Sugar Land FH. Owner est ~44yr. D-tier.','DECLINE — owner too young (~44), career-building. Recheck 20+ years.','high',0.7),
  ('81e39db8-663d-4c8c-9eaa-8f77af4c76c3','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',25.0,'Trevino Jr ~46; <53 hard gate cap. Stepfather Dale Smith may be older but not operational owner.',68.0,'2 locations (Bryan main + Madisonville) + on-site crematory + HUB-cert; $1.5-3M.',35.0,'Active in March 2025 news re tariffs = engaged; HUB-cert; not coasting.',82.0,'Bryan/College Station tier-2 +5; Brazos Valley growing.',47.0,'C_watch','19yr Bryan FH. Owner est ~46yr. C-tier.','C-tier — recheck 10-15yrs if Dale Smith retiring triggers sale.','low',0.55),
  ('2b88c0b8-5e7e-4734-94e5-cb26f869e99c','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',15.0,'Cody Jones ~40 (2014 award typically age<40); 5th gen active growth phase; <53 hard cap.',80.0,'Callaway-Jones + Cozart FH + Restever Memorial Park Cemetery; vertically integrated multi-entity.',25.0,'Tells: Harvard Mentors Program; new Funeral Center; active LinkedIn/X; growth phase.',82.0,'Bryan/College Station +5.',44.0,'D_pass','74yr Bryan FH. Owner est ~40yr. D-tier.','DECLINE — 5th gen Cody Jones ~40 in growth phase. Watch 20+ years.','medium',0.7),
  ('cf7e6394-93c4-4393-bfec-276b36e3dddf','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',88.0,'Martin Thompson ~72 (started 1976 age ~22, 50yr tenure); aging-out window.',82.0,'Multi-location (Thompson''s Harveson & Cole + Martin Thompson & Son); $4-8M est; above solo-owner.',50.0,'Tells: ''one of few remaining family-owned in DFW'' anti-corporate; 2020 intra-family acquisition; but Jon Thompson (4th gen) in business = succession pipeline = DEMOTE per instructions.',90.0,'DFW major metro 80-90 +5.',75.0,'B_forward','115yr Fort Worth FH. Owner est ~72yr. B-tier.','B-tier WATCH (demoted per instructions due to 4th-gen Jon in business). If Jon declines succession, sale plausible 24-36 months. Above solo-ETA scale.','medium',0.75),
  ('da86d9df-5339-4ac8-9980-7514c48bb829','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',15.0,'Succession completed Aug 2/2025 to young 3rd-gen (Tori HS grad ~1yr in business). <53 hard cap.',70.0,'New location opened; Henderson closed; small-scale.',20.0,'Expansion mode; young growing operators.',88.0,'DFW metro +5.',0.0,'D_pass','38yr Fort Worth FH. Owner est ~28yr. D-tier.','DECLINE — succession just completed to young 3rd-gen. Wrong timing.','high',0.85),
  ('01539cf4-9c5c-4b85-bae3-7f86e5cacfdd','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',15.0,'Joel Carver ~38; 9yr business; growth-stage; <53 hard cap.',55.0,'2 locations + low-cost positioning; $800K-2M.',20.0,'Just added managing partner 7/2024 = scaling; growth-stage disruptor.',78.0,'Amarillo tier-2.',36.0,'D_pass','9yr Amarillo FH. Owner est ~38yr. D-tier.','DECLINE — owner too young, business too new (2017). Wrong timing.','high',0.7),
  ('b6cbf710-7a64-47ae-ba41-f497b83bd30a','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',50.0,'Owner age unknown; Hispanic-surname Pasadena solo; founding year not stated (data hiding tell).',58.0,'Solo FDL likely; single Pasadena location; second-tier Harris submarket.',55.0,'Tells: founding year hidden; no FDL roster visible; anti-corporate positioning; opacity.',85.0,'Houston metro +5; Pasadena Hispanic submarket +3.',59.0,'C_watch','?yr Pasadena FH. Owner est ~Noneyr. C-tier.','Worth deep-dive via Comptroller + TFSC license for owner-age proxy. If 55+ confirmed, elevate.','low',0.35),
  ('efa6438f-b219-4098-8d59-e2dbe511e88a','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',45.0,'Owner identity not disclosed; opacity tell; year not disclosed.',70.0,'3 locations + affiliated cemetery (Dynasty Memorial Gardens); international shipping niche = repatriation cash flow.',50.0,'Tells: no founder identity; LLC structure (vs family corp = possible 2nd-gen rebrand); narrow specialty (international shipping); NFDA member.',88.0,'Houston metro +5; international repatriation niche +3.',59.0,'C_watch','?yr Houston FH. Owner est ~Noneyr. C-tier.','Niche international repatriation specialist. Worth deep-dive for owner age + valuation. Cemetery component adds value.','low',0.3),
  ('71cad209-0bf5-4676-a5f6-581e291dd3e0','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',78.0,'Linda Mitchell ~60 (35yr industry, 20yr CEO); pre-65 but high-tenure exhaustion stage.',75.0,'Solo FDL + preneed; single 15,000 sf Oak Cliff location; Black-owned historic 112-yr asset.',80.0,'Tells: no cremation services (cant compete cremation-heavy DFW); no celebration-of-life; no pet aftercare; older-style mix; no current family successor (Gary Clark exited); 20yr CEO exhaustion stage.',88.0,'Dallas major metro 85-90; Black-owned cultural niche; consolidators eyeing historic Black FHs.',79.0,'A_acquire_self','112yr Dallas FH. Owner est ~60yr. A-tier.','A-TIER PRIORITY. 112yr Oak Cliff Black-owned institution. Owner Mitchell 20yr CEO no successor. Add cremation/celebration-of-life products, modernize tech, expand to 2nd location.','medium',0.7),
  ('0fac1e08-2e0b-4c88-82d3-e4c670f7bd56','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',45.0,'Owner age unknown; founding year not disclosed.',60.0,'Single Laredo location; Hispanic surname solo-operator profile; STFDA member.',45.0,'Tells: no founder year; no chain affiliation; STFDA member implies quality but limited info.',88.0,'Laredo Webb major-metro +3 Hispanic-heavy.',55.0,'C_watch','?yr Laredo FH. Owner est ~Noneyr. C-tier.','Information-thin. Needs full enrichment (about page, license, founder identity).','low',0.25),
  ('9e46ee81-318b-41c1-9190-c4ef2cf5d428','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',65.0,'Generations tagline but current gen not named; 112yr operation. Without specific owner age, mid-band.',78.0,'2 locations + on-site crematory + preneed; ''Laredo''s oldest family-owned''; 2023 Reader''s Choice winner; SIFH+NFDA+STFDA membership = quality.',35.0,'Tells: modern service mix (live streaming, tribute videos); 2023 Reader''s Choice; active community = NOT coasting; tech-investing.',90.0,'Laredo Webb major metro 80-90; Hispanic-heavy +3.',63.0,'B_forward','112yr Laredo FH. Owner est ~Noneyr. B-tier.','B-tier WATCH. 112yr Laredo institution but NOT coasting. Strong if owner has succession gap. Needs deep-dive.','low',0.55),
  ('e008aff9-750a-45f4-911d-bb7340ae1b08','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',58.0,'Solo FDL Valdez; age unknown; need TFSC license-issue date.',58.0,'Solo FDL (sole director); Eagle Pass border-town small market; single location.',60.0,'Tells: solo-operator burnout candidate; VADEL acronym = founder identity; border-town lower competition.',88.0,'Eagle Pass Maverick border +3 Hispanic.',63.0,'B_forward','?yr Eagle Pass FH. Owner est ~Noneyr. B-tier.','Solo-operator candidate. Lower transaction multiple but lower competition. Needs deep-dive for age + property.','low',0.4),
  ('df578b86-7429-4a50-ac16-bcd9fcb3c00d','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',90.0,'Founder-widow ~73, 52-yr tenure; widow-running-solo +5; 4 adult kids in business = succession-in-motion but no decision.',85.0,'FH + Ashland Memorial Park cemetery + Harlingen Monument Company; vertically integrated; 3 locations RGV; $5-10M.',60.0,'Tells: founder-widow stage; 4-children succession question (intra-family if aligned, sale if split); vertical integration complex.',90.0,'Harlingen RGV +3 Hispanic; aging-retiree border market.',80.0,'D_pass','52yr Harlingen FH. Owner est ~73yr. D-tier.','B-tier WATCH. Founder-widow + 4 kids = succession pending. If kids split, sale to outsider in 3-5yrs. Strong vertical assets.','low',0.6),
  ('a00418ad-e3aa-41ba-94a0-c86bab174b21','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',85.0,'De Leon couple ~68 + 32-yr tenure; co-founder Garza couple already deceased (+5 founder-recently-deceased partial trigger).',80.0,'2 locations (Edinburg + San Juan); SIFH member (invitation-only quality signal); $2-4M.',60.0,'Tells: SIFH membership = quality operator (not consolidator target normally); co-founder deaths = succession pressure; founder couple 32yr in.',90.0,'Edinburg RGV Hidalgo +3 Hispanic-heavy.',77.0,'B_forward','32yr Edinburg FH. Owner est ~68yr. B-tier.','B-tier. SIFH membership + co-founder deaths suggest succession pressure building. Needs deep-dive on De Leon successor identity.','low',0.5),
  ('51a46d35-cb64-41c4-b6c7-f1686c0f2955','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',40.0,'Owner unknown; year unknown; generic brand name suggests newer entrant.',55.0,'2 locations Edinburg+Donna; small/newer competitor likely.',35.0,'Tells: generic brand ''Family'' = low-investment positioning; no founder/year disclosed; opacity.',88.0,'Hidalgo Co RGV +3 Hispanic.',49.0,'C_watch','?yr Edinburg FH. Owner est ~Noneyr. C-tier.','Skip-tier unless TFSC reveals long tenure.','low',0.2),
  ('456e867d-2e19-46d9-8669-85cb8150b60f','883fb301-0002-4bec-9478-b9d40e91f126',28.0,'Founded 2011 (15yr); outside 25-40 sweet spot. Hard gate <53 → ≤35.',55.0,'Single Conroe location; value-positioning low-margin.',30.0,'Tells: ''affordable vs corporate'' = low-margin model; newer business.',88.0,'Conroe Houston metro fast-growing +5.',44.0,'D_pass','15yr Conroe FH. Owner est ~Noneyr. D-tier.','DECLINE. Watch 10yrs.','low',0.4),
